pledged securities  we are required to pledge or otherwise restrict a portion of our cash and marketable securities as collateral for standby letters of credit, guarantees, debt, and real estate leases. we classify cash and marketable
securities with use restrictions of twelve months or longer as non-current other assets on our consolidated balance sheets. the balance of pledged securities at december31, 2008 consisted of $308 million included in other
assets. the amount required to be pledged for certain real estate lease agreements changes over the life of our leases based on our credit rating and changes in our market capitalization (common shares outstanding multiplied by the closing
