not to occupy the additional space. we also have an option to lease up to an additional approximately 500,000 square feet at rates based on fair market values at the time the option is exercised, subject to certain conditions. in addition, if
interest rates exceed a certain threshold, we have the option to provide financing for some of the buildings.  the following summarizes our
